Home >
		 Sell > Selling Your Wine 
			



 



Sell Your Wine with HDH
Hart Davis Hart’s consignment team works tirelessly to help our customers achieve record prices and the highest sell-through rates in the fine wine business. Whether your cellar is worth $10,000 or $10 million it is by any standard a significant financial asset. With the most experienced team in the wine auction business, HDH brings together private collectors, trade buyers and investors from all over the world and ensures that your collection is properly and professionally represented to bring you the highest possible return.
 



Consignment Process:
                            



Submit Your list
            Send us a list of your wine collection along with details on storage conditions and provenance to consignments@hdhwine.com, fax at 312.335.9096 or mail to 1511 W. 38th Street, Chicago, IL 60609.
             



HDH Review Process
            An HDH Specialist will undertake a thorough review of your list and provide an appraisal using the most current market data.  HDH’s pricing team, is the best in the business and will always provide you with an accurate estimate.
             



Wine Transport
            HDH will work with you to arrange shipment to our warehouse or, when appropriate, send a team to your cellar to oversee the packing and moving of your collection. We work with shipping companies all over the world and have experience with almost any shipping scenario imaginable.
             



Inspection
            HDH specialists will inspect every bottle to ensure proper condition and authenticity and to catalog conditions that will be noted for the information of the buyers.
             



Sale and Prompt Payment
            Your wine is offered to the world and sold through a live auction at award winning TRU restaurant. HDH makes prompt and full payment.
             



Consign with Confidence at HDH
We understand that the idea of moving and selling all or part of your wine collection can seem daunting. HDH keeps meticulous records of all transactions and makes the process simple and convenient for you at every step. Our consignment team is the most experienced in the industry. We know the level of care that collectors put into their cellars and we represent each collection with our unmatched professionalism and attention to detail.
Contact us
p: 312.379.8712
f: 312.335.9096
 
