Home >
		 Auction > HDH Auctions 
			



 







Hart Davis Hart’s Wine Auctions
Hart Davis Hart Wine Co. is a market leader, bringing first-rate consignments to the auction block with record results. We pride ourselves on the accuracy, efficiency and organization of our entire auction process. With over 100 years of combined experience and over 70 successful auctions we have successfully sold over $300 million of wine to participants from 30 countries and over 40 states.
We hold seven live auctions per year at award-winning  TRU restaurant, located at 676 N. St. Clair Street in the posh North Michigan Avenue retail district.  Auction catalogs and bidding are available three weeks prior to each sale. Attendance to the auction is open to the public and free of charge. Reservations for lunch at TRU during the auction ($75) should be made by calling Hart Davis Hart at 312.854.0096 or emailing info@hdhwine.com.
If you are not able to attend an auction in person, you can execute both absentee and live bids online at auction.hdhwine.com or on our mobile app. On the day of the sale, bidders can follow the auction in the salesroom, watch a video feed of the auction, and bid against the room, all in real-time. For more information, contact Hart Davis Hart at 312.482.9996 or go to auction.hdhwine.com. Hart Davis Hart also welcomes bids by phone and fax.
If you are interested in selling wine, please contact our consignment team for a complimentary appraisal.
 
