Buying from HDH Retail
Welcome to HDH Retail. Our selection includes the best of new  releases. Our inventory, as listed on www.hdhwine.com, is real-time, thoroughly inspected, in-stock and ready to ship. We apply strict standards to wine that we accept for sale, as our team of experts carefully inspects wines upon arrival in our temperature and humidity-controlled cellar.   We may occasionally offer wines on a pre-arrival basis, and these are  noted with a “P” in the wine description field. We offer highly  personalized consultation and sourcing services for buyers at every  level. Our experienced sales team can inform you about new arrivals and  recent releases, assist with special requests, or simply discuss the  latest market trends. Read some of our Customer Testimonials. 
Use any of the following methods to see our retail inventory. Results  include tasting notes and ratings from Robert Parker, Jancis Robinson,  Steve Tanzer, Allen Meadows and Wine Spectator, when available.
Download a full inventory listing in Excel or PDF format. Updated daily.
 
Retail Team
Nick Pagoria
Retail Sales Manager
312.573.2550
email
Dale Salentiny
Retail Sales Associate
312.573.5596
email
 

Customer Testimonials
We invite you to read what customers are saying about Hart Davis Hart.


 Weekly Features
Check in for our weekly features highlighting the best wines we have to offer. View our Weekly Features.
New Arrivals
We offer new arrivals frequently. Our website is real-time, so you can  be assured that you are viewing the most recent new arrivals, in-stock,  on the day they are posted to our website. View our New Arrivals.
Discounted Wines
We keep a close eye on market changes, and we adjust prices to suit the current market demand. View our Discounted Wines.
